<br>
Anyway, I'm about to go kill renux (sad, huh?). It looks like my group will be me, 60 shaman, 60 warrior, and high level cleric. Maybe a pretty uber monk too. I am told that this kind of group should have no problem getting the job done. However, I was just curious, as I've heard conflicting reports on some of these subjects....<br>
<br>
Can renux be...<br>
<br>
outrun by SoW?<br>
slowed? (i hope so)<br>
feared?<br>
rooted?<br>
snared?<br>
<br>
Any other info I would be interested in knowing? Not necessarily for this fight, but some of the up and coming rogues in my guild (we've got a 48, a 45, and a 37) will be asking for my help and advice in this same task fairly soon. Anyway, thanks in advance. Renux next, then the genreal.<br>
<br>
P.S.<br>
<br>
How often does the general drop the cazic quill?<br>
How often does the coercer drop the robe of the kedge?<br>
<br>
I do not want to go to stupid kedge keep to fight that ridiculous seahorse. Nobody ever wants to go there so I would have trouble getting any help <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uayashii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayashii</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/31/01 6:36:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> Renux can be outrun by SoW<br>
can be slowed<br>
can be feared<br>
can be rooted<br>
can be snared<br>
<br>
But as long as you have the group you mentioned, you should be able to kill Renux...... EASY. Her hp is low and if the lvl 60 warrior tank her, a lvl 55 rogue and a pretty uber monk can kill her with 2 CH at most.<br>
<br>
The drop rate of quill from General is really rare, expect it to be 1 in 10.<br>
<br>
The drop rate of KK robe from Coercer would be around 1 in 3.<br>
<br>
I would recommend you kill Coercer for robe rather than from KK. She has even higher drop rate than Phinny.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uderkan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Derkan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 11:29:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> As most rogues do, we stick together.  And 4 of my best friends in game are rogues. Needless to say, we do everything for each other.  I Have done renux , 7 times I figure. 1st time we tanked her with 2 groups and it went very well.<br>
<br>
The last 6 times we did with quick pick up groups.  However,<br>
tanking is much more fun, but you get what you can get.<br>
And this way falls right in line with us shifty types.<br>
<br>
Druid (recommend 55+)<br>
Cleric<br>
1 tank (if it goes wrong)<br>
Other than that, all rogues :)<br>
<br>
Sow everyone, buff everyone, then spawn renux.<br>
Have druid snare her, then dot her.  Kite renux around and<br>
wait about 10 seconds for aggro to fly, then all melees<br>
attack her from behind while druid continues to kite.<br>
Usually aggro will stay on druid, and it's a painless <br>
and efficient way to kill her.<br>
<br>
~As for fearing her, I have heard rumors that fearing<br>
her don't work anymore.  Can anyone shed some factual<br>
light on this.  What I was told was that in the cases where<br>
fear succeeded, it lasted only a couple of seconds.<br>
<br>
Derkan<br>
55 Rogue <br>
Lanys<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubearberry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bearberry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 2:37:14 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> Renux can be outrun by SoW<br>
can be slowed<br>
can <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> NOT</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> be feared<br>
can be rooted<br>
can be snared<br>
also<br>
can be stunned<br>
<br>
If you cast Fear on her, you get the &quot;This creature cannot be feared&quot; message.  I would assume that if she can be stunned, she can also be mezzed or charmed although I haven't tried myself <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
If you get her slowed, I would expect that your group can just tank her and beat her down.  However, I wouldn't count on slow, snare, etc sticking on the 1st, 2nd or even 3rd try.  The easiest way is aggro-kiting like Derkan described.  Chanter chaining tash works awesome for this if you have one available.  If you're going to tank, don't forget your PR buffs. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueqgalrif.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EQGalrif</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/1/01 8:22:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> Just did Renux a couple of weeks ago.  She cannot be feared anymore.  Our Druid and Enc. alternated aggro kiting duties.  Had no problem landing a snare with a 53(I think) Druid.<br>
<br>
Galrif Firlag 52nd Rake<br>
&quot;THE FOLK&quot; of Fennin Ro<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucudget.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cudget</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 10:44:18 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> In my experience, you should be able to tank her with that group.  We did it with a 56 War as tank, 55 Rogue, 48 Rogue, 50ish Cleric, late 40's Druid and 42 druid.  We took her down with out too much trouble.<br>
<br>
We did attempt it once before that, having a 3rd rogue and no cleric.  Had her down to about 10% health when we all started dropping like flies. (The 3rd rogue was the cleric and was also the one we were doing Renux for)<br>
<br>
<br>
Edit: Oh.. and if you plan to tank her.. don't try to slow too early.  She really doesn't like it, and anyone but a high tank doesn't live through quad 200 hits for very long <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucudget.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cudget</A> at: 11/2/01 10:45:29 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufhiire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fhiire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 11:43:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: renux</span><hr size=1> I just killed her last week with two groups or 55+ . eveyone says she is easy . well only if you kite her around the zone. If you try to fight her it will hurt. Try to find a druid to come with you , that will make all the differ. At least if things go bad and your war die right away , shh can run after the druid while you hit her.... She is hard to fear. but this works well. I would try to slow her too, this ,makes it easyer to run after her.- Fhire  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3195.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3199.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3183.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadCont